      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8a5f3b72-8dc9-11e2-abc6-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
