        "subject": "LU-2335 build: add script to copy client kernel code",
        "message": "LU-2335 build: add script to copy client kernel code\n\nBy running\n./build/copy-buildin <client-code-dir> <kernel-tree>\none can copy client code generated by\nbuild/build-client-source.sh into a kernel source tree.\n\nThe same script shall also take care of generating proper Kconfig\nand Kbuild files for the in-tree Lustre client.\n\nNOTE: the kernel source tree should be the same one that Lustre\nis configured against (e.g., via --with-linux= option).\n\nSigned-off-by: Peng Tao <tao.peng@emc.com>\nChange-Id: I010bd7c3f6a0b26bab5a12e572994d1bd485635b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
